{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_YY03_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x13,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Logy. Um, there's something I want to ask you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hm, something to ask me? Is it a question about weapons?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Not exactly... Um, it's about traveling."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Traveling...? What, do you intend to travel somewhere?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I'm thinking about it right now... But I have some concerns."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I've never gone that far from town before... I'm worried if I can even go on a journey..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x6b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Haha, you'd be fine. Traveling is something you get used to by doing it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Besides, you're always going outside to gather materials."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Think about it like traveling... I'd say you're already pretty accustomed to it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Uu, but... Don't you ever feel lonely when you're away from town...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "That depends on how you think about it. Personally, I think of it as part of the fun of traveling."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Huh...? What do you mean...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I start remembering people's faces during my travels. I wonder what they could be up to."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "If I do that, the next time I see them, it makes the joy of seeing them again that much stronger."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x6b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "You can't feel joy like that if you're always in town. Reunions are part of the true charm of traveling."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I see... I guess you can look at it that way..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. It's just one way of thinking, but I'd be glad if you remembered it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I got it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "If you have any other questions about traveling, come ask me anytime."
        }
    ]
}